comments: LeVert (IND) lowers his shoulder into the body of White (SAS) at the start of his drive and dislodges White from his guarding position.
LeVert (IND) swipes down and makes contact to the ball and incidental contact with the part of Gay's (SAS) hand that is considered part of the ball during his shot attempt in the post.
LeVert (IND) brings both of his hands to the ball and illegally continues his dribble.
Mills (SAS) never steps into the backcourt when he makes contact with the ball to keep it in the frontcourt.
Sumner (IND) does not beat Gay (SAS) to the spot and makes contact with his body that affects his driving shot attempt.
Replay review of the foul called on Sumner (IND) pursuant to a coach?s challenge was deemed unsuccessful.  Sumner extends his arm into DeRozan (SAS) and affects his driving shot attempt.
Poeltl (SAS) makes contact to the front of Turner's(IND) body during his shot attempt in the post.
DeRozan (SAS) makes contact to Turner's (IND) arm and affects his ability to get to the pass.
Mills (SAS) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Holiday (IND) firms up and absorbs the contact.
Turner (IND) is in the lane for longer than three seconds.
Turner(IND) places a forearm against White's (SAS) back and marginal contact occurs as he pursues the rebound.
Turner (IND) cleanly dislodges the ball from DeRozan (SAS) during his driving shot attempt.
Poeltl (SAS) commits a take foul on Holiday (IND).
